raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Hellooo!
Mabel: Hi
Mabel: img: mabel/97
Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm2: *creak*
- Nice headphones
	Player: Nice headphones
	Mabel: Oh I completely forgot I had those on
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm1: *creak*
	Mabel: My neighbor has been just a little noisy
	Mabel: And I'm trying to do my assignment
- Looking tired
	Player: Looking tired
	Mabel: Yeah.. I am
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm6: *creak*
	Mabel: My neighbor has been just a little noisy
	Mabel: I wasn't able to nap properly after class
Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm3: *creak*
Player: Srsly? 😓
Mabel: Don't worry, I'll be fine
Mabel: sfx3: bedcreakm2: *creak*
Mabel: sfx3: bedcreakm2: *creak*
Mabel: Thought: Is he tossing and turning in bed?
Mabel: Thought: I'm so confused
- Why not knock and ask them to stop lol
	Player: Why not knock and ask them to stop lol
	Mabel: Yeah that's me!
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm4: *creak*
	Mabel: Mabel who's a pro at confronting strangers and telling them to pipe down! 😵
	Mabel: Sorry, I'm just tired and it's the last thing on my mind to do
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm2: *creak*
	Mabel: Maybe if I run into him... or her?
	Mabel: Whoever is noisy
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm3: *creak*
- What's he doing?
	Player: What are they doing? It's a guy right?
	Mabel: I don't know!? And yeah I think so
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm1: *creak*
	Mabel: Maybe moving his bed around?
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm4: *creak*
	Mabel: I can't tell if there's another person but omg
	Mabel: It's like too late to be doing anything at all tbh
	Player: In Mabel time, for sure
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm3: *creak*
	Mabel: Mabel time zone ends at 8pm every day 😆
Player: Well good luck, hopefully it'll be quiet soon
Mabel: I hope so too
Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm3: *creak*
Mabel: sfx: coveredmoanm2: Ughh...
Mabel: Thought: Was that someone's voice?
Mabel: Whatever is happening is tiring me out more 😴
Mabel: Anything fun going on in your club?
Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm6: *creak*
- Not really
	Player: Not really
	Mabel: I see
- Not much, you?
	Player: Not much, you?
	Mabel: Uhh I went to visit the club house today
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm2: *creak*
	Mabel: It was really big, much bigger than photography club
	Player: Oh that's cool, anything to do there?
	Mabel: Didn't seem so lively during the day but it looked fancier than where I am now
	Mabel: Thought: Jessica was right.. it is definitely an upgrade
	Mabel: Thought: They also gave me a box of clothes that I'm supposed to wear from now on
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm6: *creak*
	Mabel: Thought: Not sure how I'm gonna get through the week ugh
Mabel: I have a paper to turn in tomorrow so I'll be up just a little longer
Mabel: sfx: bedcreakm2: *creak*
Player: Alright! Good night
Mabel: Good night 😮‍💨
=> END"
